      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, car lovers! It truly breaks my heart to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to experience the magic. I\u2019ve babied this ride since day one\u2014always garaged, hand-washed every Sunday, and treated like a member of the family. It\u2019s in absolutely stunning shape, looking just as fresh as the day it rolled off the lot. You won\u2019t find a smoother drive or a cleaner interior anywhere nearby. Come by for a coffee and a chat, and see for yourself why I\u2019m so proud of this one!",
