    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a surgically maintained E46 M3, a true purist's specimen featuring the legendary S54 power plant. This unit has undergone a comprehensive top-tier refresh, including a full VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement to ensure peak structural integrity and eliminate common chassis fatigue. The engine exhibits perfect compression across all six cylinders, delivering a linear power curve and visceral throttle response that modern turbocharged units simply cannot replicate. It sits on a precision-tuned suspension setup that optimizes roll center and reduces unsprung weight for razor-sharp turn-in. The Getrag manual gearbox is tight, with zero synchro grind, paired with a limited-slip differential that provides exceptional mechanical grip. This is a turn-key, investment-grade machine dialed in for the most demanding driver.",
      "price": 49250.0,
